gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 112, Suns 100
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeated the Suns, 112-100. Joel Embiid led the 76ers with 26 points (3-3 3PT FG), 11 rebounds, and three assists as Kelly Oubre Jr. (25 points, 10-18 FG) and Tyrese Maxey (22 points, 10 assists, five rebounds) totaled 47 points for Philadelphia. Kevin Durant led Phoenix with 31 points and eight rebounds. The 76ers improve to 4-1 as the Suns fall to 2-4.
